    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/4692b42df68c001c87d8fa13fa4bc3e5.poster.avif?t=1762864561\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/4692b42df68c001c87d8fa13fa4bc3e5.webm?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/4692b42df68c001c87d8fa13fa4bc3e5.mp4?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/6ecf3df6c53d3c7d176dc76a229bc5bc.avif?t=1762864561\" width=616 height=102 /></span>一场可怕的风暴令四周的海洋怒涛汹涌，将你的大船抛入附近岛屿的危险岩石中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >醒来后，你发现自己的船只徒留碎片，撞毁在一个满是……青蛙的陌生小岛上？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >意大利面交易网将带你踏遍这座陌生的岛屿，寻找材料来修理你的船。在探索《Time on Frog Island》世界的过程中，你将邂逅许多友好的角色，解决烧脑难题，发现隐秘宝藏以及更多乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/48a8a40824e4c8444b3deec2e095612e.poster.avif?t=1762864561\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/48a8a40824e4c8444b3deec2e095612e.webm?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/48a8a40824e4c8444b3deec2e095612e.mp4?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/6ab2ecd2ebdff26df247ae4941cd6d86.avif?t=1762864561\" width=616 height=102 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个岛屿沙盒中走出自己的道路——你永远不知道下一个拐角会出现什么！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结交原住民青蛙，尽你所能帮助他们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过捕鱼和耕种发现新的物品，创造简单的混合物，改变你在岛上的移动方式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向青蛙学习，并在岛上测试你的新技能。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/ab3bc3c0d27417fd7cf0f740621fa942.poster.avif?t=1762864561\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/ab3bc3c0d27417fd7cf0f740621fa942.webm?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/ab3bc3c0d27417fd7cf0f740621fa942.mp4?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/f2df966cdb57b32cb6468e293caf278d.avif?t=1762864561\" width=616 height=102 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >四处询问你需要的物品，但记住，你可能需要帮助青蛙才能得到你想要的东西。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >破解有趣的谜题，获得所需的物品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽量不要太过沉迷于岛屿生活哦！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/240eaf81d2d492a69e5e490c80d0a1a0.poster.avif?t=1762864561\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/240eaf81d2d492a69e5e490c80d0a1a0.webm?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/240eaf81d2d492a69e5e490c80d0a1a0.mp4?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/6ec19b11949a230c31badc488835f1a9.avif?t=1762864561\" width=616 height=102 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跑得更快，跳得更高，摔得更轻——只要携带合适的物品，一切皆有可能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现各种不同的方法来完成重要交易。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你捡到的每件东西都可能成为获得更大东西的关键所在。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/6642a38b8edc2e5538d6eda5d943894b.poster.avif?t=1762864561\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/6642a38b8edc2e5538d6eda5d943894b.webm?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717510/extras/6642a38b8edc2e5538d6eda5d943894b.mp4?t=1762864561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
